## API Routes (current)

| Route | Auth | Purpose |
|-------|------|---------|
| `POST /api/analyze` | Yes | STT + 3 judges + save `sessions` (`feature: speech_eval`) |
| `POST /api/speak` | No* | ElevenLabs TTS for judge playback |
| `POST /api/generate-topic` | Rate limit | Topic suggestions |
| `GET /api/voice-coach/signed-url` | Yes | ElevenLabs ConvAI signed URL + `mode` + `memory` |
| `POST /api/voice-coach/end-session` | Yes | Summarize transcript, save session + memory + tasks |
| `GET /api/voice-coach/history` | Yes | Past voice sessions |
| `PATCH /api/voice-coach/tasks` | Yes | Mark homework complete |
| `GET /api/speech-eval/history` | Yes | Past panel sessions |
| `POST /api/profile` | Yes | Create/update `profiles.username` |

\*`speak` is rate-limited; panel runs only for signed-in users in practice.

