## LLM — OpenAI primary, Groq fallback

```typescript
async function getJudgeFeedback(system: string, user: string): Promise<string> {
  try {
    const res = await getOpenAI().chat.completions.create({
      model: 'gpt-4o',
      messages: [
        { role: 'system', content: system },
        { role: 'user', content: user },
      ],
      max_tokens: 280,
      temperature: 0.75,
    })
    return res.choices[0]?.message?.content?.trim() ?? ''
  } catch {
    const res = await getGroq().chat.completions.create({
      model: 'llama-3.3-70b-versatile',
      messages: [
        { role: 'system', content: system },
        { role: 'user', content: user },
      ],
      max_tokens: 280,
      temperature: 0.75,
    })
    return res.choices[0]?.message?.content?.trim() ?? ''
  }
}
```

- Run Counter, Grammarian, Evaluator in parallel: `Promise.all([...])`
- Judge copy is **spoken** via TTS — natural sentences, ~5–7 sentences, no markdown (see prompts in `app/api/analyze/route.ts`)
- Voice coach summaries: `lib/summarize-voice-session.ts`; memory: `lib/build-coach-memory.ts`

