## Speech-to-Text (`/api/analyze`)

1. **Whisper** (`getOpenAI().audio.transcriptions`) first — saves ElevenLabs credits
2. **ElevenLabs STT** fallback: `POST …/v1/speech-to-text`, `model_id=scribe_v1`
3. Reject unclear audio via `assessTranscriptQuality()` (`422`, `code: unclear_audio`)

