## Text-to-Speech (`/api/speak`)

```
POST https://api.elevenlabs.io/v1/text-to-speech/{voiceId}
Headers: xi-api-key, Content-Type: application/json, Accept: audio/mpeg
Body: { text, model_id: "eleven_multilingual_v2" }
```

Default judge voice IDs live in `lib/speech-eval.ts` (`DEFAULT_VOICES`); users can pick alternates in the Recorder UI. Do not change IDs without updating that file and testing playback.

