## Voice Coach (ElevenLabs ConvAI)

- Agent env: `ELEVENLABS_VOICE_COACH_AGENT_ID` — must be **Public** in ElevenLabs dashboard for WebRTC
- Dynamic variables: `mode`, `memory` — system prompt in `lib/voice-coach-agent-prompt.ts`
- Client connects via signed URL from `GET /api/voice-coach/signed-url?mode=…`
- Persist **only on End session** (`POST /api/voice-coach/end-session`), not per message; draft recovery: `lib/voice-coach-draft.ts`

Errors: `lib/elevenlabs-errors.ts`, `lib/voice-coach-connection-errors.ts`

