## Supabase Schema (auth + RLS)

| Table | Notes |
|-------|--------|
| `profiles` | `id` → `auth.users`, unique `username` |
| `sessions` | `user_id`, `feature` (`speech_eval` \| `voice_coach`), judge columns, `evaluator_score`, `filler_word_count`, voice fields (`mode`, `summary`, `strengths`, `weaknesses`, `elevenlabs_conversation_id`) |
| `action_points` | Homework tasks; `session_id`, `mode`, `task`, `completed` |
| `user_coach_memory` | Per-user `memory_blob`, `current_goal`, `difficulty` |

RLS: users read/write **own rows** only (`auth.uid() = user_id`). Server routes use the user’s Supabase session cookie via `createClient()` from `@/lib/supabase/server`.

Migrations: `supabase/migrations/`. Full write/read map: `docs/supabase-persistence.md`.

