## Environment Variables (`.env.local` only)

See `.env.example`. Server-only: `OPENAI_API_KEY`, `GROQ_API_KEY`, `ELEVENLABS_API_KEY`, `ELEVENLABS_VOICE_COACH_AGENT_ID`. Client: `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL`, `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY`. Restart `npm run dev` after changes.
